Package: llegir
Title: Deterministic Evidence and Model-Assisted Interpretation of Gene Co-Expression Modules
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person('Sam', 'Morabito', email = 'smorabit82@gmail.com', role = c('aut', 'cre'))
Description: Loads a gene co-expression module object (hdWGCNA first), gathers a
    standardized bundle of evidence per module via a toolbox of deterministic R
    functions, and drafts an evidence-backed interpretation paragraph via a
    model-agnostic synthesis layer with faithfulness checking, confidence fusion,
    and confidence-gated human review. The deterministic evidence core has no
    model dependency; synthesis backends are pluggable (an offline mock backend,
    and live structured-output backends via 'ellmer'). Experimental: the public
    API is not yet stable.
